Twelfth Avenue, east side, north from and across W. 47th Street, showing demolition in progress for the widening of this thoroughfare. The 4 story stable seen in No. 633 W. 47th Street. North of same is the former Hardman, Peck and Co. factory on 48th Street.
Accompanying this photostat is a negative print.

March 20, 1935.
Views 1 and 2.

P. L. Sperr
